## Review Policy
"PRs com findings de severidade CRITICAL do BugBot
nao podem ser mergeados sem ao menos um comentario
humano respondendo diretamente ao finding."

## Review Process
1. Review the PR
2. Check for findings of severity CRITICAL from BugBot
3. If there are any, comment on the PR with a human response addressing the finding
4. Merge the PR if there are no critical findings or if the human response addresses the finding

## Review Criteria
1. The PR must be free of critical findings from BugBot
2. The PR must have a human response addressing any critical findings
